28:22.577 --> 28:24.079
I'm sorry, Gisela.

28:24.120 --> 28:27.248
But I have a new team now,
and I moved on.

28:29.751 --> 28:32.295
[sentimental music]

28:32.337 --> 28:35.590
- So wanted to touch base
real quick

28:35.632 --> 28:38.551
about everything
that happened...

28:38.593 --> 28:40.720
and was said on stage,

28:40.762 --> 28:43.348
particularly by me...

28:43.390 --> 28:44.891
about you.

28:44.933 --> 28:46.726
- Well, it was life-changing.

28:46.768 --> 28:48.353
I have you to thank.

28:48.395 --> 28:50.230
Sorry I disappeared
back there.

28:50.271 --> 28:54.901
I was just scouted
by a record label based in LA.

28:54.943 --> 28:56.069
They love my song.

28:56.111 --> 28:57.821
- What?
- Yeah. [laughs]

28:57.862 --> 28:59.447
- Heidi, that's huge.

28:59.489 --> 29:00.699
- Yeah.

29:00.740 --> 29:03.410
- Wait, so are--
are you moving to LA?

29:03.451 --> 29:07.580
'Cause that is very,
very far from here, he guessed.

29:07.622 --> 29:09.040
- I don't know.

29:09.082 --> 29:11.084
I mean, it's everything
I've ever dreamed of.

29:11.126 --> 29:15.547
But the question is,
will.i.am or won't.i.am?

29:15.588 --> 29:16.756
- Totally.
I get that.

29:16.798 --> 29:18.174
Believe me.
I've been there.

29:18.216 --> 29:22.762
But did you happen
to "Fergie"--t

29:22.804 --> 29:25.015
about the other stuff I said?

29:26.182 --> 29:30.228
'Cause I can repeat it
if you need me to.

29:33.815 --> 29:35.567
I meant every word of it.

29:39.320 --> 29:40.613
- Bumper.

29:40.655 --> 29:41.865
You better not be thinking

29:41.906 --> 29:43.116
of running away
from our sham marriage.

29:43.158 --> 29:45.035
- Oh, great.
My wife's here.

29:45.076 --> 29:47.287
- Here's a list of rules
for a living in my house.

29:47.328 --> 29:49.122
I'm very particular,
and I've got

29:49.164 --> 29:50.582
something called white mold.

29:50.623 --> 29:53.251
It happens when ham sits
too long on your walls.

29:53.293 --> 29:55.211
- Okay.
I have to move in with you?

29:56.171 --> 29:58.798
- Uh, well, yeah, of course.

29:58.840 --> 30:00.300
You have to stay in Berlin

30:00.342 --> 30:02.886
and sell the marriage,
or else we both

30:02.927 --> 30:04.137
are getting arrested for fraud.

30:04.179 --> 30:06.139
Oh, and my girlfriend Ilse
gets the bed.

30:06.181 --> 30:09.142
You are on
a very hard concrete pullout.

30:09.184 --> 30:11.811
Heidi,
what an epic performance.

30:11.853 --> 30:13.480
I'm so happy for you.

30:13.521 --> 30:14.564
- Thanks.

30:14.606 --> 30:17.233
I'm so happy for both of you.

30:17.275 --> 30:19.736
- There's my constellation.

30:19.778 --> 30:21.279
[laughter]

30:21.321 --> 30:24.908
Oh, that was an incredible day,
huh?

30:24.949 --> 30:26.409
- [sighs]
- Yeah.

30:26.451 --> 30:29.746
- I don't know
what's gonna happen next,

30:29.788 --> 30:32.624
but I am so grateful
I came here.

30:32.665 --> 30:34.167
[upbeat electronic music]

30:34.209 --> 30:37.045
Shit.
I forgot to call about my cat.

30:37.087 --> 30:44.219
* *
